            <title><![CDATA[【图集】解放军在台周边展开军事演训行动]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-08/china-taiwan-us-diplomacy-military-035054.jpg?VersionId=a9P7s2wNPDUt_8SQHCgMET18I51otFP_&amp;itok=XAtDdXk3" title="一架中国军用直升机星期四（8月4日）飞过福建平潭上空，吸引游客驻足观察。（法新社）" alt="一架中国军用直升机星期四（8月4日）飞过福建平潭上空，吸引游客驻足观察。（法新社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-08/china-taiwan-us-diplomacy-military-035054.jpg?VersionId=a9P7s2wNPDUt_8SQHCgMET18I51otFP_&amp;itok=XAtDdXk3" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
